_metadata.description: HAR file analysis optimized for AI interpretation. Includes pre-computed indexes, normalized entities, relationship graphs, performance budgets, query examples, JSON Schema, data quality metrics, and search indexes.

_usage.quickAccess: Use _indexes for fast lookups by domain, status, or pattern
_usage.budgets: Use _budgets to check if metrics meet performance thresholds
_usage.examples: Use _queryExamples for query patterns and code snippets
_usage.schema: Use _schema for type definitions and validation
_usage.quality: Use _dataQuality for completeness and confidence scores

_compression.compressionRatio: Removing body fields can reduce size by ~60-80%
